  "name": "RPlog_All_the_Baron_s_Men",
  "title": "All the Baron's Men",
  "summary": "On a Nar Shaddaa landing pad, gamblers Sorin and his Twi'lek associate Suana arrive to take possession of the YT-2400 freighter they won from Baron Songir, met by Yeoman Valya to complete the ship transfer. Knowing the Baron has discovered their registry forgery, the pair are caught off guard when a turbolift disgorges four of the Baron's thugs holding the captured party-girl grifter Aisaiy. A firefight erupts across the walkway as Suana picks off the enforcers one by one and Aisaiy fumbles her hold-out blaster, while Valya scrambles to ready the half-closed ship. Amid the chaos Aisaiy pitches Valya a job offer mid-battle, and the pilot defects to their crew. With all four thugs down and reinforcements arriving, the group hauls Sorin aboard and Valya blasts the newly acquired freighter off the pad, leaving the Baron's men behind.",
